Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor

Provides the classes and interfaces of the HOBO Direct Mechanism API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for general description).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DBuilder
    Provides mechanisms for building the HOBO direct model, together with the associated Frames Model (FM) to which it is bound (represented respectively via DModel and CModel objects).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DClassMap
    Represents a set of mappings between an Object Model (OM) class (a DObject-derived class) and entities in one or more external sources.
    DFieldMap
    Represents a mapping between an Object Model (OM) field (a DField-derived class) and a correponding entity in an external source.
    DModelMap
    Represents all required mappings between specific entities in the Object Model (OM) and correponding entities in any external sources that will also be contributing towards the Frames Model (FM).

Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor Description

Provides the classes and interfaces of the HOBO Direct Mechanism API (see uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for general description).

NOTE: This is a companion package to the uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model package, with which it shares circular dependencies at the implementation level, though not at the API level. See uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo for further details.
